>>> Before annotating:

Select the categories you need:
+ Create a proper .txt file containing labels (check format in 'changecategories.py') in the working dir
$ cd <this-folder>
$ python changecategories.py <label-file-name>

Set up the configurations you need:
$ cd <this-folder>
$ python setconfig.py <img-folder-name>


